    <sparkle:version>16</sparkle:version>
    <sparkle:shortVersionString>4.0.0-beta.05</sparkle:shortVersionString>
    <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>12.3</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
    <sparkle:channel>beta</sparkle:channel>
    <description><![CDATA[
      <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; padding: 12px; }
        h3 { font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 6px 0; }
        h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
        ul { padding-left: 18px; margin: 4px 0; }
        li { margin: 4px 0; line-height: 1.5; }
      </style>
      <h3>Fixed</h3><ul> <li><b>Cmd+Q and Escape now trigger unsaved changes warning</b> — previously bypassed the save dialog and closed the editor without warning.</li> <li><b>Lasso selection disabled for pencil/marker</b> — Shift+drag in pencil and marker tools now constrains to straight lines as expected, instead of triggering the lasso marquee selection.</li> <li><b>Recording HUD spacing</b> — reduced excess padding on the right side of the timer for balanced layout.</li>  </ul><h3>Translations</h3><ul> <li><b>17 new strings translated</b> across 40 languages: save dialog (Save & Close, Discard), recording controls (Stop/Pause/Resume), translation engine settings, webcam labels.</li></ul>
    ]]></description>
